{"tid":1955730,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港股上市發達大法","createTime":"2020-04-02T16:23:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T00:53:02.000Z","uid":81236,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6b1f4150be756f8d4aa613c8ff9613049c665e9f","tid":1955730,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T16:23:37.000Z","msg":"一上就話派特別息，收市即除淨，派淨股價0.01<br />\n<br />\n之後彈弓手話都係唔派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再拎啲錢聽日回購由0.01掃上去<br />\n<br />\n再派息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重覆數十次應該仲好用過十合一再一供十<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ada0f5e09f2d23d15710de2dc68d2259e3d8407","tid":1955730,"uid":9264,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T16:32:36.000Z","msg":"你唔發達正契弟"},{"pid":"62d050207722ddfcfca22d0d7e628be5db568cc6","tid":1955730,"uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T16:34:32.000Z","msg":"你真係天才<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6c1f0135e1b180cd9a0afe687f19067016e7e47a","tid":1955730,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:51:21.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d498ec318c7290a4c6d5a895a97d389438c4e2","tid":1955730,"uid":222907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:53:02.000Z","msg":"匯控（0005）彈弓手不派發2019年第四次中期股息，然而股價經已除淨，港交所（0388）發言人表示，不評論個別公司，僅稱當股票發行人宣布派發現金股息時，聯交所可在除淨日調整相關發行人的「前收市價」，以供市場參考。<br />\n<br />\n港交所建議股東及有意投資者買賣股份時，尤其在除淨日至有關條件達成前期間，務必謹慎行事。如有任何疑問，應諮詢相關專業顧問。<br />\n<br />\n市場上有投資者質疑匯控在除淨後才反口不派息，做法是否有問題；熟悉上市公司派息運作的卓佳商務部董事總經理鍾絳虹亦指出，「除淨」本身是市場運作一部分，是投資者將股份「在除淨日後不能收取上期股息」納有考慮後對股價的評估，只能算是影響股價的其中一項因素，亦不涉上市公司本身操作，因此無法追究。"}]}